That's amazing.

1068
00:47:05,641 --> 00:47:07,910
Childcare comes with the package.

1069
00:47:07,910 --> 00:47:09,111
I'll come along too.

1070
00:47:09,578 --> 00:47:11,981
(Eye contact)

1071
00:47:11,981 --> 00:47:13,716
Amazing.

1072
00:47:13,716 --> 00:47:16,418
- That's huge.
- Right.

1073
00:47:16,418 --> 00:47:18,120
A huge impact.

1074
00:47:18,120 --> 00:47:20,889
Another one of Jeong Yoon's strengths...

1075
00:47:20,889 --> 00:47:22,224
is that she's a great cook.

1076
00:47:22,658 --> 00:47:25,828
When I taste her cooking,
I think, "There's nothing to improve."

1077
00:47:25,828 --> 00:47:28,030
It's that good.

1078
00:47:30,699 --> 00:47:33,335
Her mother is a great cook.

1079
00:47:33,702 --> 00:47:35,237
A treasure.

1080
00:47:35,237 --> 00:47:37,239
Hurry and take Jeong Yoon.

1081
00:47:39,341 --> 00:47:40,576
Thank you.

1082
00:47:42,544 --> 00:47:44,313
About the academy,

1083
00:47:44,313 --> 00:47:46,482
do you run it as a partnership?

1084
00:47:46,482 --> 00:47:49,351
We have separate divisions
for Miss Korea and Miss Chunhyang,

1085
00:47:49,351 --> 00:47:51,420
and I oversee the Miss Korea division...

1086
00:47:51,420 --> 00:47:53,489
and run the Hakdong branch.

1087
00:47:53,489 --> 00:47:57,693
I trained about
ten Miss Korea contestants last year.

1088
00:47:57,693 --> 00:47:59,962
For your generation,

1089
00:47:59,962 --> 00:48:03,599
you can think of me
as a famous salon director.

1090
00:48:03,599 --> 00:48:06,735
To make one point in my own favor,

1091
00:48:06,735 --> 00:48:08,937
I make my own schedule,

1092
00:48:08,937 --> 00:48:11,407
so I have a lot of flexibility
with my time.

1093
00:48:11,407 --> 00:48:13,709
That means even after getting married,
while raising children,

1094
00:48:13,709 --> 00:48:16,745
I have a work setup
that lets me keep working.

1095
00:48:16,745 --> 00:48:18,447
And childcare is covered too.

1096
00:48:19,448 --> 00:48:21,216
That's really important.

1097
00:48:22,084 --> 00:48:23,285
Perfect.

1098
00:48:23,285 --> 00:48:26,789
So it's perfect. Her mom will help too.

1099
00:48:26,789 --> 00:48:28,657
She has so much going for her.

1100
00:48:29,725 --> 00:48:30,926
She's in a league of her own.

1101
00:48:32,061 --> 00:48:34,830
You said your type is a masculine man.

1102
00:48:34,830 --> 00:48:36,031
How would you define that?

1103
00:48:36,532 --> 00:48:39,868
There are so many kinds of masculine men.

1104
00:48:39,868 --> 00:48:41,637
When I'm with a man,

1105
00:48:41,637 --> 00:48:44,740
I like feeling more feminine.

1106
00:48:44,740 --> 00:48:48,477
I get a little more of a spark...

1107
00:48:48,477 --> 00:48:50,579
when I can care for and support him.

1108
00:48:50,579 --> 00:48:52,181
I like a man who can lead me...

1109
00:48:52,181 --> 00:48:53,983
and whom I can care for...

1110
00:48:53,983 --> 00:48:57,653
in a way that helps him shine
even brighter.

1111
00:48:57,653 --> 00:48:58,887
She's so perfect.

1112
00:48:59,555 --> 00:49:00,322
Nice.

1113
00:49:00,322 --> 00:49:03,325
- She's like the ideal homemaker.
- The ideal homemaker.

1114
00:49:03,859 --> 00:49:05,160
What are your hobbies?

1115
00:49:05,627 --> 00:49:07,096
My hobbies are...

1116
00:49:07,096 --> 00:49:08,831
playing with my dog at home,

1117
00:49:09,365 --> 00:49:12,735
walking around the neighborhood,
and traveling.

1118
00:49:12,735 --> 00:49:14,870
If your dog and...

1119
00:49:14,870 --> 00:49:16,472
your boyfriend...

1120
00:49:16,472 --> 00:49:18,340
both need your time,

1121
00:49:18,340 --> 00:49:20,309
which one would get more of your time?

1122
00:49:20,309 --> 00:49:22,244
I can take the dog with me
and look after it.

1123
00:49:23,445 --> 00:49:24,980
I love them equally.

1124
00:49:24,980 --> 00:49:27,082
So you couldn't choose?

1125
00:49:27,082 --> 00:49:29,251
When I'm dating,

1126
00:49:29,251 --> 00:49:30,686
my boyfriend tends to be my top priority.

1127
00:49:32,421 --> 00:49:33,622
Thank you.

1128
00:49:33,622 --> 00:49:37,793
(All the women's details are revealed.)

1129
00:49:38,627 --> 00:49:40,095
It must be hard to choose.

1130
00:49:41,163 --> 00:49:42,898
Their credentials are so impressive.

1131
00:49:43,699 --> 00:49:46,568
There are so many impressive women here,

1132
00:49:46,568 --> 00:49:49,038
it won't be easy to choose.

1133
00:49:49,038 --> 00:49:50,472
That's what I thought.

1134
00:49:50,472 --> 00:49:53,475
They're all impressive,
and they have great jobs.

1135
00:49:53,475 --> 00:49:56,512
I'm interested in every one of them.

1136
00:49:56,512 --> 00:49:59,348
All the women's jobs are out in the open.

1137
00:49:59,348 --> 00:50:02,318
I think the mothers will probably favor...

1138
00:50:02,318 --> 00:50:04,420
Ha Yoon.

1139
00:50:04,420 --> 00:50:05,587
The Korean medicine doctor.

1140
00:50:05,587 --> 00:50:07,556
Moms tend to like professional jobs.

1141
00:50:07,556 --> 00:50:10,793
And stability as well.

1142
00:50:10,793 --> 00:50:13,729
So I think the Korean medicine doctor
and the Samsung employee...

1143
00:50:13,729 --> 00:50:16,298
may attract the most votes.

1144
00:50:16,965 --> 00:50:18,901
(The date selection begins
after the women's introductions.)

1145
00:50:18,901 --> 00:50:20,636
It looks like it's date-picking time.

1146
00:50:21,337 --> 00:50:22,838
For today's date selection,

1147
00:50:22,838 --> 00:50:24,707
the men's mothers will choose.

1148
00:50:27,576 --> 00:50:28,911
For this date,

1149
00:50:28,911 --> 00:50:30,346
regardless of what their sons want,

1150
00:50:30,346 --> 00:50:35,250
only the mothers' choices will decide it.

1151
00:50:35,250 --> 00:50:37,987
Mothers and sons...

1152
00:50:37,987 --> 00:50:39,655
can't discuss it with each other.

1153
00:50:39,655 --> 00:50:42,358
The men's mothers will choose now.

1154
00:50:42,358 --> 00:50:44,493
I'm calling three votes
for the Korean medicine doctor.

1155
00:50:46,328 --> 00:50:47,696
But wait.

1156
00:50:48,397 --> 00:50:49,898
Though, there is this.

1157
00:50:49,898 --> 00:50:51,767
If her profile is too impressive,

1158
00:50:51,767 --> 00:50:54,937
they might worry their sons
might feel a little intimidated.

1159
00:50:54,937 --> 00:50:56,305
Maybe that's why...

1160
00:50:56,305 --> 00:50:58,407
- the votes won't all go her way.
- That could happen.

1161
00:50:58,407 --> 00:51:00,409
Still, I think she'll get a lot of votes.

1162
00:51:03,545 --> 00:51:07,449
Mothers, choose the woman
you'd like your son to date,

1163
00:51:07,449 --> 00:51:09,418
and stand beside her.

1164
00:51:11,754 --> 00:51:13,322
Mom, smile even if no one picks me.

1165
00:51:14,089 --> 00:51:14,957
Smile.

1166
00:51:15,691 --> 00:51:17,226
They're all such strong contenders,

1167
00:51:17,660 --> 00:51:19,128
so honestly, I'm not confident.

1168
00:51:19,395 --> 00:51:21,797
I got two votes yesterday,

1169
00:51:21,797 --> 00:51:24,667
so I feel anxious
that the number could go down.

1170
00:51:25,467 --> 00:51:27,302
It's here. This is my moment.

1171
00:51:27,302 --> 00:51:31,073
I'm more confident
with mothers than with men.

1172
00:51:31,440 --> 00:51:37,012
(Date partners are chosen
solely by the mothers.)

1173
00:51:37,379 --> 00:51:40,816
(Who will the men's mothers choose?)

1174
00:51:46,689 --> 00:51:48,824
(First to go, Lee In Kwon's mother)

1175
00:51:48,824 --> 00:51:51,393
It's In Kwon's turn.

1176
00:51:53,362 --> 00:51:54,363
I'm scared.

1177
00:51:55,564 --> 00:51:57,900
- It had been Do Yoon all along.
- Right.

1178
00:51:58,467 --> 00:52:00,936
Do Yoon is so pretty,

1179
00:52:00,936 --> 00:52:04,273
and seems well educated
and from a good family.

1180
00:52:04,273 --> 00:52:05,941
So I liked her,

1181
00:52:05,941 --> 00:52:08,711
but In Kwon is the type
who needs to take the lead,

1182
00:52:08,711 --> 00:52:12,748
and Jeong Yoon says she adjusts to others.

1183
00:52:12,748 --> 00:52:14,950
So I thought she might be
a good match for In Kwon.

1184
00:52:15,617 --> 00:52:16,852
This way.

1185
00:52:16,852 --> 00:52:19,321
(Lee In Kwon and his mother set off.)

1186
00:52:23,892 --> 00:52:26,996
I'm hoping there'll be
at least one vote for me.

1187
00:52:26,996 --> 00:52:29,231
I hope it's In Kwon.

1188
00:52:33,035 --> 00:52:37,306
(Who will Lee In Kwon's mother choose?)

1189
00:52:40,876 --> 00:52:43,812
(Ahn Do Yoon, who clicked with her son
from the beginning?)

1190
00:52:43,812 --> 00:52:47,116
(Or Choi Jeong Yoon,
who seems like a good match for him?)

1191
00:52:51,487 --> 00:52:56,892
(She heads in the opposite direction
from Do Yoon.)

1192
00:53:03,232 --> 00:53:05,601
- Hello.
- Hello.

1193
00:53:07,670 --> 00:53:09,805
Hello.

1194
00:53:10,706 --> 00:53:15,678
(Lee In Kwon's mother
chooses Choi Jeong Yoon.)

1195
00:53:15,678 --> 00:53:18,881
Jeong Yoon said things
that really appealed to mothers.

1196
00:53:18,881 --> 00:53:21,016
She says her boyfriend comes first,

1197
00:53:21,016 --> 00:53:24,320
she can make time and adjust her schedule,

1198
00:53:24,320 --> 00:53:25,954
and she can cook.

1199
00:53:25,954 --> 00:53:28,390
I think the mothers' hearts...

1200
00:53:28,390 --> 00:53:30,893
were really swayed.

1201
00:53:31,760 --> 00:53:34,530
Thanks to my mother,
we're finally getting a chance to talk.

1202
00:53:34,530 --> 00:53:36,198
We barely got to talk yesterday.

1203
00:53:40,536 --> 00:53:42,037
She doesn't have to feel too disappointed.

1204
00:53:42,037 --> 00:53:44,373
- This was his mother's pick.
- Yes.

1205
00:53:45,975 --> 00:53:46,976
Thank you.

1206
00:53:47,910 --> 00:53:51,847
My interest in Jeong Yoon really went up.

1207
00:53:51,847 --> 00:53:54,683
She seems like an ideal wife
and daughter-in-law.

1208
00:53:55,551 --> 00:53:57,753
She's not like young women these days.

1209
00:53:57,753 --> 00:53:59,254
That made me like her more,

1210
00:53:59,254 --> 00:54:02,224
and I hope In Kwon gets to talk with her.

1211
00:54:02,958 --> 00:54:04,660
I never saw that coming.

1212
00:54:06,929 --> 00:54:08,364
It's not that you hated the idea, right?

1213
00:54:08,364 --> 00:54:09,264
No.

1214
00:54:09,264 --> 00:54:11,667
You barely asked any questions,
that's why.

1215
00:54:13,669 --> 00:54:15,804
Jeong Yoon was saying
she wanted to talk to him too.

1216
00:54:15,804 --> 00:54:16,705
Really?

1217
00:54:16,705 --> 00:54:18,741
They hadn't spoken even once.

1218
00:54:29,251 --> 00:54:31,120
(Second to go, Kwon Ye Chan's mother)

1219
00:54:31,120 --> 00:54:35,224
Now, our popular guy, Ye Chan.

1220
00:54:36,025 --> 00:54:38,093
I'd like to go on a date
with Do Yoon today,

1221
00:54:38,093 --> 00:54:39,595
if I get the chance.

1222
00:54:39,595 --> 00:54:42,564
She seems like she's worked really hard...

1223
00:54:42,564 --> 00:54:45,601
at a very sought-after company
without stopping,

1224
00:54:45,601 --> 00:54:47,770
so I'd like to talk to her about that.

1225
00:54:48,537 --> 00:54:50,072
Who will Ye Chan's mother choose?

1226
00:54:50,072 --> 00:54:52,941
She may make a different choice.

1227
00:54:52,941 --> 00:54:56,245
(Who will Kwon Ye Chan's mother choose?)

1228
00:55:00,549 --> 00:55:04,720
(She passes her son's pick, Ahn Do Yoon.)

1229
00:55:04,987 --> 00:55:08,524
(Could it be Kang Hyeon,
who liked Ye Chan?)

1230
00:55:15,431 --> 00:55:18,567
(She passes Lee Kang Hyeon.)

1231
00:55:19,168 --> 00:55:21,136
- Where is she going?
- Is this right?

1232
00:55:22,037 --> 00:55:26,542
(Could Choi Jeong Yoon
get two votes again?)

1233
00:55:26,775 --> 00:55:28,377
Am I supposed to stand behind you?

1234
00:55:29,511 --> 00:55:30,446
Thank you.

1235
00:55:30,446 --> 00:55:31,480
My gosh.

1236
00:55:32,648 --> 00:55:33,582
My goodness.

1237
00:55:34,984 --> 00:55:36,952
I knew this would happen.

1238
00:55:37,419 --> 00:55:39,688
You should go over there.

1239
00:55:39,688 --> 00:55:42,992
That's not the right place.

1240
00:55:42,992 --> 00:55:44,059
No?

1241
00:55:44,059 --> 00:55:45,227
It isn't?

1242
00:55:45,227 --> 00:55:47,062
- That's not the right place?
- Ma'am.

1243
00:55:47,062 --> 00:55:49,298
She startled me.

1244
00:55:49,298 --> 00:55:52,201
She mixed up the direction.

1245
00:55:53,335 --> 00:55:58,774
(Who will Kwon Ye Chan's mother
really choose?)

1246
00:56:02,077 --> 00:56:03,445
In the end...

1247
00:56:03,445 --> 00:56:04,380
The Korean medicine doctor?

1248
00:56:11,020 --> 00:56:12,021
Are you sure?

1249
00:56:12,488 --> 00:56:13,789
Are you sure?

1250
00:56:13,989 --> 00:56:16,992
(Kwon Ye Chan's mother
chooses Yang Ha Yoon.)

1251
00:56:16,992 --> 00:56:18,394
Nice to meet you.

1252
00:56:18,394 --> 00:56:20,295
Yes, Doctor.

1253
00:56:20,295 --> 00:56:21,263
Of course.

1254
00:56:21,263 --> 00:56:23,365
It was easy to see coming.

1255
00:56:23,365 --> 00:56:24,600
There was a detour.

1256
00:56:26,535 --> 00:56:28,337
(After a brief detour,
she reaches Ha Yoon's mother.)

1257
00:56:28,337 --> 00:56:29,338
Thank you.

1258
00:56:30,205 --> 00:56:32,541
- I was nervous.
- Were you?

1259
00:56:32,541 --> 00:56:33,709
Personally,

1260
00:56:33,709 --> 00:56:35,978
I like professionals.

1261
00:56:35,978 --> 00:56:38,113
I really do,

1262
00:56:38,113 --> 00:56:40,349
as a match for Ye Chan.

1263
00:56:40,349 --> 00:56:42,117
We were saying earlier...

1264
00:56:42,117 --> 00:56:45,287
that he is some kind of
a licensed professional.

1265
00:56:45,287 --> 00:56:47,156
That's what we were saying.

1266
00:56:47,156 --> 00:56:48,190
So she wants his wife
to have a professional title too.

1267
00:56:48,190 --> 00:56:50,826
She might think they'd be a good fit,
both being professionals.

1268
00:56:50,826 --> 00:56:51,694
I'm jealous.

1269
00:56:52,294 --> 00:56:56,065
For a moment,
I thought my mother had chosen Jeong Yoon,

1270
00:56:56,065 --> 00:56:57,166
so I went and stood beside her.

1271
00:56:57,166 --> 00:56:59,835
But she was still walking past.

1272
00:56:59,835 --> 00:57:02,237
Looking back,

1273
00:57:02,237 --> 00:57:04,540
maybe my subconscious belief...

1274
00:57:04,540 --> 00:57:07,609
that Jeong Yoon was my top choice
made me do that.

1275
00:57:09,244 --> 00:57:11,380
(Third to go, Kim Dong Young's mother)

1276
00:57:11,380 --> 00:57:12,348
Dong Young.

1277
00:57:13,048 --> 00:57:15,184
I hope she picks someone else.

1278
00:57:19,588 --> 00:57:22,491
After the introductions,
the person I like most...

1279
00:57:22,491 --> 00:57:23,492
is Ha Yoon.

1280
00:57:24,126 --> 00:57:25,260
No.

1281
00:57:26,128 --> 00:57:27,296
I knew it.

1282
00:57:28,030 --> 00:57:31,500
She seems really dedicated to her work,

1283
00:57:31,500 --> 00:57:34,536
and she has qualities
that keep making me more curious.

1284
00:57:35,938 --> 00:57:36,772
My goodness.

1285
00:57:36,772 --> 00:57:38,207
What about his mother?

1286
00:57:38,207 --> 00:57:41,543
(Who will Kim Dong Young's mother choose?)

1287
00:57:43,812 --> 00:57:45,881
(She passes Ahn Do Yoon.)

1288
00:57:49,485 --> 00:57:51,720
(She passes Kim Da Hye.)

1289
00:57:51,720 --> 00:57:54,323
His mother liked Ha Yoon from the start.

1290
00:57:54,323 --> 00:57:57,159
Now that she knows she's a Korean medicine
doctor, I think she likes her even more.

1291
00:58:01,730 --> 00:58:02,965
Where are you going?

1292
00:58:04,466 --> 00:58:06,168
(Kim Dong Young's mother
chooses Yang Ha Yoon.)

1293
00:58:06,168 --> 00:58:07,903
Yes, as expected.

1294
00:58:08,771 --> 00:58:10,673
It is Ha Yoon, as expected.

1295
00:58:11,340 --> 00:58:13,208
- We have competition.
- Thank you.

1296
00:58:15,544 --> 00:58:16,812
Thank you, everyone.

1297
00:58:17,780 --> 00:58:19,548
Thank you, mothers.

1298
00:58:19,548 --> 00:58:21,016
It's because you are so wonderful.

1299
00:58:21,016 --> 00:58:21,950
Not at all.

1300
00:58:23,052 --> 00:58:24,453
The picks keep overlapping.

1301
00:58:24,453 --> 00:58:25,954
I'll take good care of her.

1302
00:58:26,488 --> 00:58:29,224
Every little thing Ha Yoon did...

1303
00:58:29,224 --> 00:58:32,094
felt sweet and endearing.

1304
00:58:32,094 --> 00:58:34,496
Even with her professional career,

1305
00:58:34,496 --> 00:58:38,233
she's so humble,
and that made me like her even more.

1306
00:58:38,233 --> 00:58:42,037
I predicted three votes earlier.

1307
00:58:42,037 --> 00:58:44,707
Will she really get all three?

1308
00:58:44,707 --> 00:58:46,041
That would be incredible.

1309
00:58:46,709 --> 00:58:49,144
I can't get over how charming she is.

1310
00:58:49,144 --> 00:58:50,045
Yes.

1311
00:58:50,412 --> 00:58:52,448
I brought some Gyeongokgo.

1312
00:58:52,448 --> 00:58:54,416
- I'll give it to you later.
- Thank you.

1313
00:58:54,817 --> 00:58:58,554
(The three women still awaiting a pick)

1314
00:59:00,556 --> 00:59:02,191
It's okay.

1315
00:59:02,558 --> 00:59:05,027
(Ahn Do Yoon, 0 votes)

1316
00:59:05,027 --> 00:59:08,130
Do Yoon, Da Hye,
and Kang Hyeon are still at zero.

1317
00:59:08,130 --> 00:59:10,299
Yes, zero votes.

1318
00:59:11,367 --> 00:59:14,470
I have no idea what you're thinking, Mom.

1319
00:59:14,470 --> 00:59:16,639
I gave it a lot of thought.

1320
00:59:16,639 --> 00:59:19,341
Who should I choose?

1321
00:59:19,341 --> 00:59:22,645
For now, Kim Da Hye is still my top pick.

1322
00:59:22,645 --> 00:59:23,479
He's still fixated on Da Hye.

1323
00:59:23,479 --> 00:59:25,781
Her introduction made her seem
even more appealing,

1324
00:59:25,781 --> 00:59:27,783
and I...

1325
00:59:27,783 --> 00:59:28,984
like her even more now.

1326
00:59:30,285 --> 00:59:34,390
(Fourth to go, Kang Shin Woo's mother)

1327
00:59:36,025 --> 00:59:41,897
(The three women
who have not been chosen yet)

1328
00:59:41,897 --> 00:59:43,365
It's hard to hide my feelings.

1329
00:59:45,434 --> 00:59:49,805
(Mothers of zero-vote women
feel their children's pain.)

1330
00:59:50,172 --> 00:59:52,574
- Are you nervous?
- Yes, I'm nervous.

1331
00:59:52,658 --> 00:59:54,512
(Who will Kang Shin Woo's mother choose?)

1332
00:59:55,139 --> 00:59:58,209
(Her son's pick, Kim Da Hye?)

1333
00:59:58,209 --> 01:00:01,212
Who will she choose?

1334
01:00:04,915 --> 01:00:10,187
(She passes her son's pick, Kim Da Hye.)

1335
01:00:13,624 --> 01:00:16,227
There's another contender.

1336
01:00:16,994 --> 01:00:19,363
(She passes Yang Ha Yoon.)

1337
01:00:21,498 --> 01:00:22,399
This way.

1338
01:00:24,401 --> 01:00:25,502
Another contender.

1339
01:00:26,303 --> 01:00:27,805
She went to Jeong Yoon.

1340
01:00:27,805 --> 01:00:31,041
Jeong Yoon is popular.

1341
01:00:31,675 --> 01:00:33,244
Mom, over here. Hello.

1342
01:00:33,244 --> 01:00:35,145
(Choi Jeong Yoon receives 2 votes.)

1343
01:00:35,145 --> 01:00:39,950
(The mother's choice
differs from her son's.)

1344
01:00:39,950 --> 01:00:43,821
Thank you so much.

1345
01:00:43,821 --> 01:00:45,356
I could only watch the mom.

1346
01:00:47,191 --> 01:00:52,062
I think Jeong Yoon has been
hugely helped by her mother.

1347
01:00:52,062 --> 01:00:54,098
Starting with that talk about chili paste
and soybean paste on Day One.

1348
01:00:54,098 --> 01:00:55,866
Right. She was so appealing.

1349
01:00:55,866 --> 01:00:59,136
And she said, "I'll help raise the kids."

1350
01:00:59,136 --> 01:01:00,871
- That's not something everyone says.
- Right.

1351
01:01:00,871 --> 01:01:04,041
When the mothers sat together
and introduced them yesterday,

1352
01:01:04,041 --> 01:01:05,943
that's when her score shot up.

1353
01:01:05,943 --> 01:01:06,877
Really?

1354
01:01:06,877 --> 01:01:08,612
(Nod)

1355
01:01:08,612 --> 01:01:10,814
Actually, last night,

1356
01:01:10,814 --> 01:01:13,450
I flirted by mentioning
chili paste and soybean paste.

1357
01:01:13,450 --> 01:01:14,685
- Exactly.
- Right.

1358
01:01:15,486 --> 01:01:17,087
I may not look it,

1359
01:01:17,087 --> 01:01:20,491
but I make chili paste and soybean paste.

1360
01:01:20,491 --> 01:01:22,993
They say you can tell
what a daughter is like by her mother.

1361
01:01:22,993 --> 01:01:24,528
She really won me over.

1362
01:01:24,528 --> 01:01:27,798
I chose Jeong Yoon
because I liked her mother so much.

1363
01:01:28,499 --> 01:01:29,600
You're popular.

1364
01:01:29,600 --> 01:01:30,768
Me?

1365
01:01:30,768 --> 01:01:33,003
Maybe Mom promoted me well.

1366
01:01:33,003 --> 01:01:34,438
(The power of fermented-paste flirting?)

1367
01:01:34,438 --> 01:01:37,174
If they all go that way,

1368
01:01:38,776 --> 01:01:40,444
that's not good.

1369
01:01:41,445 --> 01:01:46,150
(The choices pile up
around Yang Ha Yoon and Choi Jeong Yoon.)

1370
01:01:46,150 --> 01:01:49,954
Those two have very strong advantages.

1371
01:01:49,954 --> 01:01:53,924
One has the kind of career moms love.

1372
01:01:53,924 --> 01:01:55,392
Right.

1373
01:01:55,392 --> 01:01:57,962
And the other comes with
the kind of family setup they'd love...

1374
01:01:57,962 --> 01:02:01,465
- their sons to have if they got married.
- He'd be loved so much.

1375
01:02:01,465 --> 01:02:04,535
They both have serious advantages.

1376
01:02:05,002 --> 01:02:07,071
What do we do? Only one left.

1377
01:02:07,972 --> 01:02:10,908
Only Moon Seong Mo's mother remains.

1378
01:02:12,009 --> 01:02:13,944
What if you get three votes?

1379
01:02:13,944 --> 01:02:15,546
No.

1380
01:02:15,546 --> 01:02:18,282
(Will the choices pile up again?)

1381
01:02:18,449 --> 01:02:21,619
(Or will a new date come together?)

1382
01:02:24,722 --> 01:02:29,860
(Last to go, Moon Seong Mo's mother)

1383
01:02:33,163 --> 01:02:34,198
How did this happen?

1384
01:02:35,332 --> 01:02:36,367
After hearing the introductions,

1385
01:02:36,367 --> 01:02:39,537
I thought I'd most like to talk to Da Hye.

1386
01:02:39,537 --> 01:02:40,371
Really?

1387
01:02:40,371 --> 01:02:42,039
Fifteen body-profile shoots...

1388
01:02:42,039 --> 01:02:43,841
isn't something just anyone can pull off.

1389
01:02:43,841 --> 01:02:45,543
So I got curious,

1390
01:02:45,543 --> 01:02:48,679
and her fitness background
really appealed to me.

1391
01:02:49,713 --> 01:02:51,615
It could be Da Hye or Jeong Yoon.

1392
01:02:54,151 --> 01:02:59,890
(Will the son and mother
make the same choice?)

1393
01:03:01,251 --> 01:03:04,854
Who will Moon Seong Mo's mother choose?

1394
01:03:07,731 --> 01:03:10,568
(She passes Ahn Do Yoon.)

1395
01:03:14,939 --> 01:03:19,443
(She passes her son's pick, Kim Da Hye.)

1396
01:03:23,447 --> 01:03:26,584
(She heads toward the end.)

1397
01:03:26,584 --> 01:03:28,886
(Could it be again...)

1398
01:03:31,822 --> 01:03:33,524
Maybe the fourth person, Kang Hyeon?

1399
01:03:34,291 --> 01:03:38,262
I'm such a devoted daughter.
Maybe one mother will still pick me.

1400
01:03:38,262 --> 01:03:40,865
I want to get to know Seong Mo more,

1401
01:03:40,865 --> 01:03:43,133
so I hope we get a chance to go on a date.

1402
01:03:44,802 --> 01:03:50,841
(Will Seong Mo's mother
head toward Kang Hyeon?)

1403
01:03:52,109 --> 01:03:53,477
She turned.

1404
01:03:53,477 --> 01:03:54,712
She turned!

1405
01:03:54,712 --> 01:03:56,680
(A sudden change of direction)

1406
01:03:59,385 --> 01:04:00,920
That's totally unexpected.

1407
01:04:01,454 --> 01:04:02,621
Here.

1408
01:04:02,621 --> 01:04:04,156
Thank you.

1409
01:04:04,557 --> 01:04:05,658
Here.

1410
01:04:05,658 --> 01:04:06,859
Thank you.

1411
01:04:06,859 --> 01:04:07,927
(Moon Seong Mo's mother
chooses Kim Da Hye.)

1412
01:04:07,927 --> 01:04:09,662
Did she know what her son was feeling?

1413
01:04:09,662 --> 01:04:10,830
They must have
communicated telepathically.

1414
01:04:12,832 --> 01:04:16,869
I think she sensed
a work-related connection,

1415
01:04:16,869 --> 01:04:20,740
because Da Hye has a job...

1416
01:04:20,740 --> 01:04:24,143
that seems to suit her son very well.

1417
01:04:24,143 --> 01:04:27,146
Seong Mo loves working out,

1418
01:04:27,146 --> 01:04:28,814
and Da Hye works in that world.

1419
01:04:28,814 --> 01:04:30,883
His sister is a Pilates instructor too.

1420
01:04:30,883 --> 01:04:32,284
They have something in common.

1421
01:04:32,284 --> 01:04:33,552
His sister? I see.

1422
01:04:33,552 --> 01:04:36,522
I chose Da Hye because I wanted
to give her and Seong Mo a chance.

1423
01:04:36,822 --> 01:04:39,458
Mom had the same thought as me? Amazing.

1424
01:04:39,458 --> 01:04:40,693
Was it telepathy?

1425
01:04:40,693 --> 01:04:41,861
Telepathy.

1426
01:04:43,029 --> 01:04:44,263
They look cute.

1427
01:04:45,331 --> 01:04:46,565
They look cute together.

1428
01:04:47,833 --> 01:04:49,802
I thought a lot of people
would be standing here.

1429
01:04:50,903 --> 01:04:52,304
Thanks for that prediction.

1430
01:04:53,673 --> 01:04:55,975
(Glances)

1431
01:04:55,975 --> 01:04:57,977
Shin Woo doesn't look happy.

1432
01:04:57,977 --> 01:04:59,779
- Poor Shin Woo.
- He looks like he might cry.

1433
01:05:00,613 --> 01:05:03,649
(The men's mothers
have finished choosing.)

1434
01:05:03,649 --> 01:05:04,917
So this is how it turned out.

1435
01:05:04,917 --> 01:05:07,987
I thought Do Yoon
would be the most popular.

1436
01:05:08,921 --> 01:05:12,091
(Men's mothers' picks,
Ahn Do Yoon, 0 votes)

1437
01:05:12,091 --> 01:05:16,062
(Lee Kang Hyeon, 0 votes)

1438
01:05:16,062 --> 01:05:17,830
But Do Yoon...

1439
01:05:17,830 --> 01:05:18,998
It's her age.

1440
01:05:18,998 --> 01:05:19,999
She's the youngest.

1441
01:05:19,999 --> 01:05:22,001
There's also one more factor.

1442
01:05:22,001 --> 01:05:24,170
- She lives in Dongtan.
- Because she lives in Dongtan...

1443
01:05:24,170 --> 01:05:25,438
So maybe...

1444
01:05:25,438 --> 01:05:26,472
Long-distance is tough.

1445
01:05:26,472 --> 01:05:30,476
Driving all the way to Dongtan
and back to take her home...

1446
01:05:30,476 --> 01:05:33,379
might be exhausting.
That may have factored in too.

1447
01:05:33,379 --> 01:05:34,880
Kang Hyeon...

1448
01:05:34,880 --> 01:05:37,683
constantly emphasizing
that she's a devoted daughter...

1449
01:05:37,683 --> 01:05:40,152
may not play well here.

1450
01:05:40,152 --> 01:05:42,388
They may worry
their son will have a hard time.

1451
01:05:42,388 --> 01:05:43,522
That's...

1452
01:05:50,996 --> 01:05:52,198
What was the issue?

1453
01:05:52,198 --> 01:05:55,134
It gave me a lot to rethink.

1454
01:05:55,134 --> 01:05:58,904
Maybe they didn't like
that I'm a freelancer.

1455
01:05:58,904 --> 01:06:02,274
What bothered them? Did they not like me?

1456
01:06:02,274 --> 01:06:04,410
I had all kinds of thoughts.

1457
01:06:04,410 --> 01:06:07,380
But with Mom there, it was really hard.

1458
01:06:07,380 --> 01:06:11,484
Seeing Mom standing there alone
really weighed on me.

1459
01:06:19,392 --> 01:06:21,560
During the mothers' introductions,

1460
01:06:21,560 --> 01:06:25,131
a few moms really sold their daughters.

1461
01:06:25,131 --> 01:06:28,000
It was the mothers choosing,

1462
01:06:28,000 --> 01:06:30,336
so I think that affected things a lot.

1463
01:06:30,336 --> 01:06:32,638
I felt sorry for Do Yoon.

1464
01:06:37,076 --> 01:06:39,245
For anyone hoping to find
a match with their parents,

1465
01:06:39,245 --> 01:06:41,614
the doors of Match to Marry
are always open.

1466
01:06:41,614 --> 01:06:43,949
Don't hesitate to apply below.

1467
01:06:44,383 --> 01:06:46,018
It really feels like a blind date.

1468
01:06:46,018 --> 01:06:47,453
You look like Gong Seung Yeon.

1469
01:06:47,453 --> 01:06:49,588
- That was...
- So out of the blue.

1470
01:06:49,588 --> 01:06:50,489
(The contestants start
being more proactive.)

1471
01:06:50,489 --> 01:06:52,892
I was set on Do Yoon,
but after talking to Jeong Yoon,

1472
01:06:52,892 --> 01:06:53,893
I think I need to give it more thought.

1473
01:06:53,893 --> 01:06:55,061
He can't make up his mind.

1474
01:06:55,061 --> 01:06:56,629
The vibe can't help but be good.

1475
01:06:56,629 --> 01:06:58,931
The more I get to know her,
the more curious I get.

1476
01:06:58,931 --> 01:07:00,199
What do I do?

1477
01:07:00,199 --> 01:07:02,034
They're both so great.

1478
01:07:02,034 --> 01:07:05,337
Cupid's arrows are flying
in every direction.

1479
01:07:05,337 --> 01:07:07,740
The men will now choose
their dinner dates.

1480
01:07:07,740 --> 01:07:09,909
(The men's choices could overturn
the mothers' picks.)

1481
01:07:09,909 --> 01:07:10,910
There's no way to predict it.

1482
01:07:10,910 --> 01:07:11,844
This is my chance.

1483
01:07:11,844 --> 01:07:14,213
Will mothers and sons
make the same choices?

1484
01:07:14,714 --> 01:07:15,715
Where is he going?

1485
01:07:15,715 --> 01:07:16,682
My gosh.

1486
01:07:16,682 --> 01:07:17,817
This is insane.

1487
01:07:18,651 --> 01:07:19,685
(What will the men choose
to shock everyone?)
